I seem to recall
an ancient legend about that.

35
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,400
I remember too.

36
00:01:53,410 --> 00:01:57,120
A magical talisman
far beneath Lavan's kingdom.

37
00:01:57,110 --> 00:01:58,190
What does it do?

38
00:01:58,190 --> 00:01:59,660
According to the legend,

39
00:01:59,660 --> 00:02:03,110
it's the source from which our
magic wands draw their power.

40
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,590
Maybe if we can bring
the wands to it,

41
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:07,510
we can recharge
them with magic!

42
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:09,370
Well, what are we waiting for?

43
00:02:09,370 --> 00:02:10,620
Let's get moving.

44
00:02:13,210 --> 00:02:14,870
What is it?

45
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:17,220
