The Heart of Ponyland.

70
00:03:58,980 --> 00:04:00,310
(All gasp in amazement)

71
00:04:01,530 --> 00:04:03,400
Now I remember.

72
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,980
According to the legend,

73
00:04:04,990 --> 00:04:06,960
we have to lay
our wands in the crowns

74
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,330
and then their power
will be restored.

75
00:04:09,330 --> 00:04:11,250
Well, no time like the present.

76
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:16,640
Oh, no!
It's Lavan!

77
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,580
Get away from there.

78
00:04:18,580 --> 00:04:21,420
(All scream)

79
00:04:23,390 --> 00:04:24,640
(All scream)

80
00:04:25,890 --> 00:04:28,260
(Evil laugh)

81
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:30,180
Oh, with every new minute,

82
00:04:30,180 --> 00:04:33,350
I learn how to control
my powers more.

83
00:04:33,350 --> 00:04:37,070
You have no chance!

84
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:38,940
Oh! What's going to happen?

85
00:04:38,940 --> 00:04:40,440
Lavan controls
the high ground.

86
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,410
He can stay where he is
and pick us off,

87
00:04:42,410 --> 00:04:44,910
or he can come down and get us.

88
00:04:44,910 --> 00:04:46,530
What else can he do?

89
00:04:46,530 --> 00:04:48,490
He could give up.

90
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:49,760
(All scream)
Ah!

91
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:52,750
But I don't think
we should count on that.

92
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:57,010
I'm gonna make
one last surveillance flight

93
00:04:57,010 --> 00:04:59,020
before we return to the others.

94
00:04:59,010 --> 00:05:00,920
Be careful, Wind Whistler.

95
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,550
(struggles)

96
00:05:08,550 --> 00:05:10,430
Wind Whistler!

97
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:14,030
Oh!
I-I can't move it.

98
00:05:14,020 --> 00:05:15,270
Go get the others.

99
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:17,860
But there's not enough time!

100
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:20,360
By the time
I get back with help...

101
00:05:24,030 --> 00:05:25,450
Ooh, we're done for now.

102
00:05:25,450 --> 00:05:28,030
