(whispering)

108
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:44,000
Ponies! Surrender!
And I might let you live!

109
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,890
Never!

110
00:05:45,890 --> 00:05:46,890
(laughs)

111
00:05:46,890 --> 00:05:49,260
If that's how you want it...

112
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:57,180
Charge! Bushwoolies!

113
00:05:57,180 --> 00:05:58,480
(All)
Yeah! Yeah! Yeah!

114
00:05:59,070 --> 00:06:00,350
Oh boy, Charge!

115
00:06:00,350 --> 00:06:02,180
Yeah, Bushwoolies
like to charge.

116
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:03,500
Yeah, yeah, charge, charge!
Let's go! Yeah.

117
00:06:04,110 --> 00:06:05,360
Uh-oh...

118
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:07,200
(Lavan groans)

119
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:09,080
Drop those wands!

120
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:10,280
Nah! I just made it!

121
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:12,860
(Bushwoolies taunt)

122
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,830
Get to the Heart.

123
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:20,180
I'll take care of Lavan.

124
00:06:22,010 --> 00:06:23,520
(roars)

125
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:34,350
Yay!

126
00:06:34,350 --> 00:06:35,690
Yeah, yay!

127
00:06:35,690 --> 00:06:36,890
Uh-oh!

128
00:06:36,890 --> 00:06:39,470
(ice crackles)

129
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:42,020
Stop!

130
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:44,700
Quickly!
We must work together.

131
00:06:50,290 --> 00:06:53,830
(laughs loudly)

132
00:06:55,710 --> 00:06:59,880
No!
No!

133
00:07:01,550 --> 00:07:03,220
He's gone.

134
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:04,470
(tremoring)
(All gasp)

135
00:07:04,470 --> 00:07:08,930
Yeah, and we will be too unless
we fix Ponyland's magic.

136
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:11,250
(tremoring continues)
Let's put our wands
together again.

137
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:19,480
(struggles)
Uhh! Uhh!

138
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,400
Wind Whistler, look!

139
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:31,440
What does it mean,
Wind Whistler?

140
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,940
It means everything
is all right now, Locket.

141
00:07:38,530 --> 00:07:41,750
Oh, my, my, my!
Oh, this is powerful magic.

142
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:44,370
The most powerful
there is, Habbit.

143
00:07:44,370 --> 00:07:48,010
Oh, well, Magic
can't fix everything.

144
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,970
Everything's back to normal.

145
00:07:52,970 --> 00:07:54,270
I can sense it.

146
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:57,940
We could not have defeated Lavan
without your help, Bushwoolies.

147
00:07:57,940 --> 00:08:00,980
(All)
Aww, shucks... It's nothing...

148
00:08:00,970 --> 00:08:03,860
In return for your bravery,
we knight you.

149
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:06,360
Henceforth, you shall
guard these crowns

150
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,230
as we guard the magic wands.

151
00:08:10,620 --> 00:08:12,320
- Wow! Yay!
- Bushwoolies like it.

152
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,910
- Watch 'em close!
- Yeah!

153
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:15,700
I will keep this last one,

154
00:08:15,710 --> 00:08:20,550
in memory of the Bushwoolie who
was lost in the Jewel Desert.

155
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:25,040
Uh, does anyone have any idea
how we get out of here?

156
00:08:26,420 --> 00:08:27,760
That's easy, Spike.

157
00:08:29,970 --> 00:08:32,750
Goodbye, my friends.

158
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,100
Come back and visit
the new kingdom

159
00:08:34,090 --> 00:08:37,470
