and the Ice Orgs.

160
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:47,910
(giddy laughter)

161
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:51,150
Well, the magic has been put
right in Ponyland again

162
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:53,030
and Lavan is no more.

163
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,920
Our quest is over.

164
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:58,030
We never did decide
who should be queen.

165
00:08:58,030 --> 00:09:00,530
I know!
Let's all take turns.

166
00:09:00,530 --> 00:09:02,420
- Good idea!
- Perfect!

167
00:09:02,420 --> 00:09:03,670
(All giggle)
A terrific idea.

168
00:09:05,540 --> 00:09:08,300
It's too bad
about that poor Bushwoolie.

169
00:09:08,290 --> 00:09:11,040
It's also too bad that
I lost the Rainbow of Light.

170
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:13,540
We'll never find
it in the desert.

171
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:17,140
(gasps)
Hey, everybody, look!

172
00:09:17,130 --> 00:09:19,010
(All gasp)
Oh!

173
00:09:19,020 --> 00:09:21,890
Here, Megan, Rainbow of Light.

174
00:09:21,890 --> 00:09:24,200
(sighs)
Bushwoolie bushed!

175
00:09:24,190 --> 00:09:26,110
What for dinner?

176
00:09:26,110 --> 00:09:27,970
(gobbling and murmering)

177
00:09:28,610 --> 00:09:29,730
(burps)

178
